text.tspan: Simply relaxing in the garden and watching the quiet,
clean lawn mower doing the work? Or moving freely
without cable salad while trimming your hedge or drilling
holes for a shelf? Cordless, electric tools are in trend.
Conversely, combustion-powered tools are a thing of the
past. They are noisy and pollute. Instead, we can see
strong growth for green power tools equipped with eff
cient brushless motors and long-lasting batteries.
